    "impact": "If a valid or compromised factory mints a loan to an existing vETH pair, the pair's ERC20 balance increases while its reserves remain stale. The next swap can treat the newly minted debt as input and withdraw the paired quote token, while the added vETH remains debt-locked. This can drain or severely corrupt existing launch-pair reserves.",
